text: Jonab Ali Ukil is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Rangpur-3. ==Career== Ukil was elected to parliament from Rangpur-3 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Jonab Ali Ukil
